
'''Xolile Tshabalala''' (yavutse ku ya 9 Mata 1977) ni umukinnyi wa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo.  Azwiho uruhare muri serivise nyinshi za tereviziyo zizwi cyane zirimo ''4Play:Sex Tips for Girls'', ''Secrets & Scandals'', ''Blood & Water'' and ''Housekeepers''.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i Vrede, muri Leta y'Ubuntu.  Yiswe  na nyirakuru ubyara se. Yarangije mu Ishuri Rikuru ry’Ubuhanzi  afite icyubahiro ndetse na 'Best Performer Performer'. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu masomo ye mu ishuri ry’igihugu, Xolile yagize amahirwe yo gukina na Thembi Mtshali-Jones, ari naho yamubereye umujyanama. Bakinnye hamwe mu ikinamico ''Crucible'' yerekanwe ku Isoko ry'Isoko . Uyu mukinnyi wa filime nawe yakinnye. Yakinnye kandi mubikorwa byinshi bya Televiziyo nka, na Soul City season 7, aho yakinnye mushiki we Zama. Ntabwo bigarukira gusa kuri ecran , Xolile yakinnye kandi mumikino itandukanye irimo "Undi Mwana".  

Mu 2005, yafashe ikiruhuko cyo gukina. Nyuma yagiye muri [[Amerika]] kwitabira ishuri rya Filime rya New York . Yagarutse muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo mu mwaka wa 2010 akina 'Noma' muri televiziyo ya ''4Play: Sex Tips for Girls.'' Hanyuma yakinnye cyane yerekana 'Mandi Mbalula' muri serial ''Fallen'', ikinamico yo mu 2011. Muri 2013, Xolile yagaragaye nka 'Gugu' muri ''High Rollers'' yacaga kuri SABC 3.  

